\c 2
\s Kubata ushe kwaJehovha pamazuva okupedzisira
\p
\v 1 Shoko rakaonekwa naIsaya, mwa nakomana waAmozi, pamusoro paJudha neJerusarema.
\v 2 Pamazuva okupedzisira zvichaitika kuti gomo reimba yaJehovha richasimbiswa pamusoro pamakomo, richakwiridzwa kupfuura zvikomo; marudzi ose achamhanyira kwariri.
\v 3 Vanhu vazhinji vachaendako vachiti, Uyai, ngatikwire kugomo raJehovha, kuimba yaMwari waJakove; iye achatidzidzisa nzira dzake, tichafamba mumakwara ake; nekuti murayiro uchabva paZiyoni, shoko raJehovha richabva Jerusarema.
\v 4 Iye achatonga pakati pamarudzi, nokururamisira vanhu vazhinji; vachapfura minondo yavo vachiita mapadza, namapfumo avo vachiaita mapanga okuchekerera miti; rumwe rudzi harungazosimudziri rumwe rudzi munondo, havangazodzidzi kurwa.
\s Valsiraeri ngavadzokere kuna Jehovha, varase zvifananidzo zvavo
\p
\v 5 Iwe imba yaJakove, uyai tifambe muchiedza chaJehovha.
\v 6 nekuti imwi Jehovha makasiya vanhu venyu veimba yaJakove, nekuti vazere netsika dzinobva mabvazuva, vanouka savaFirisitia, vanobatana maoko navana vavatorwa.
\p
\v 7 Nyika yavo izere nesirivha nendarama, fuma yavo haiperi; nyika yavo izerewo namabhiza, nengoro dzavo dzokurwa hadziperi.
\v 8 Nyika yavo izerewo nezvifananidzo; vanonamata zvakaitwa namaoko avo, izvo zvakaitwa nemimwe yavo.
\p
\v 9 Vanhu vaduku vakakotamiswa, navakuru vakaninipiswa; saka musavakanganwira.
\p
\v 10 Pinda mudombo uvande,muguruva, nokuda kwaJehovha anotyisa, uye nokuda kokubwinya koumambo hwake.
\v 11 Kuzvikudza kwavanhu kuchaderedzwa, namanyawi avanhu achaninipiswa, Jehovha oga achakudzwa nezuva iro.
\v 12 nekuti Jehovha wehondo ane zuva rake pamusoro pavose vanodada navanozvikudza, navana manyawi; vachaderedzwa;
\v 13 napamusoro pemisidhari yose yeRebhanoni yakareba yakakwirira; napamusoro pamiouki yose yeBhashani,
\v 14 napamusoro pamakomo ose marefu, napamusoro pezvikomo zvose zvakakwirira,
\v 15 napamusoro peshongwe dzose refu, napamusoro pamasvingo ose akasimbiswa,
\v 16 napamusoro pezvikepe zvose zveTarishishi, napamusoro pezvifananidzo zvose zvinofadza.
\v 17 Ukuru hwevanhu huchakotamiswa, nokuzvikudza kwavanhu kuchaderedzwa; Jehovha oga achakudzwa nezuva iro.
\p
\v 18 Zvifananidzo zvichapera chose.
\v 19 Vanhu vachapinda mumapako amabwe, nomumakomba muvhu, nokuda kwaJehovha anotyisa, uye nokuda kokubwinya koumambo hwake, kana achisimuka kuzunungusa nyika nesimba.
\v 20 Nezuva iro vanhu vacharasa zvifananidzo zvavo zvesirivha nezvifananidzo zvavo zvendarama, zvavakazviitira kuti vazvinamate, vachizviisa kunhuta nezviremwaremwa;
\v 21 vapinde mumapako amabwe, nomumikaha yamabwe makuru, nokuda kwaJehovha anotyisa, uye nokuda kokubwinya koumambo hwake, kana achisimuka kuzunungusa nyika nesimba.
\p
\v 22 Regai munhu, anokufema mumhino dzake; nekuti anobatsireiko?
